<title>NEW ZEALAND: S&amp;P assigns AA- long term rating to Wgtn council.</title>
<headline>S&amp;P assigns AA- long term rating to Wgtn council.</headline>
<dateline>WELLINGTON 1997-07-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Wellington Regional Council (WRC) said on Tuesday that credit rating agency Standard and Poor's had given it an AA- credit rating for long term debt.</p>
<p>WRC said that rating ranked its capacity to pay alongside trading banks, and well above many of New Zealand's major corporates.</p>
<p>The council's rating for short-term debt is A-1+, the highest possible.</p>
<p>WRC said the AA- rating for long term debt reflected its consistent budgetary performance, conservative financial management and strong commitment to financial planning.  </p>
